14
00:00:51,605 --> 00:00:54,190
50% of your sample may be controls.

15
00:00:54,190 --> 00:00:59,180
When you sample on disease status you can
no longer validly estimate things like

16
00:00:59,180 --> 00:01:01,740
the risk of the disease or the prevalence
