19
00:01:09,500 --> 00:01:13,280
the only valid measure of relative risk is
the odds ratio.

20
00:01:13,280 --> 00:01:16,250
The odds ratio can therefore be applied in
the case control study, and

21
00:01:16,250 --> 00:01:19,510
since it's the only relative risk that
