36
00:02:08,860 --> 00:02:13,830
So if you have a two by two table, you can
say well, you have, you either are exposed

37
00:02:13,830 --> 00:02:18,850
or not, and you have the outcome or not,
any two binary variable will work there.

38
00:02:18,850 --> 00:02:24,030
By convention, we sometimes call the cells
