divided by b times c.

66
00:03:49,480 --> 00:03:52,250
And it turns out that this odds ratio, the
odds of.

67
00:03:52,250 --> 00:03:56,650
Being exposed in the case version of the
control group is mathematically equivalent

68
00:03:56,650 --> 00:04:02,420
to the odds of getting the disease in the
exposed group versus the unexposed group.

69
00:04:02,420 --> 00:04:04,360
Since those are mathematically equivalent,

70
00:04:04,360 --> 00:04:08,220
that's why this is the only valid measure
