400
00:21:27,590 --> 00:21:30,940
your odds ratio might be something, you
know, like 15.

401
00:21:30,940 --> 00:21:31,890
So huge.

402
00:21:31,890 --> 00:21:33,110
A, a big distortion.

403
00:21:33,110 --> 00:21:36,090
So you're going to be careful with common
outcomes and also the bigger.

