407
00:21:47,310 --> 00:21:50,940
I just happened to be looking at something
the other day that somebody sent me

408
00:21:50,940 --> 00:21:52,860
from an, this was in their abstract, and

409
00:21:52,860 --> 00:21:55,000
I've changed things a little for anonymity
